@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Shipping Agent Rep." as Actor
participant "User Interface\n(Single Page App)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System REST API)" as Backend

Actor -> UI : 1: create/submit notification
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (POST/PATCH /api/notifications)
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (201 Created / 204 No Content)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Actor : 1.3: Display confirmation
deactivate UI

@enduml